text: Gamze () is a female Turkish given name. It denotes the dimple on someone's cheek when he or she smiles. It's considered as a feature of beauty. People named Gamze include: * Gamze Bezan (born 1994), Turkish footballer * Gamze Bulut (born 1992), Turkish middle distance runner * Gamze İskeçeli (born 1983), Turkish footballer * Gamze Nur Yaman (born 1999), Turkish women's footballer * Gamze Özçelik (born 1982), Turkish actress * Gamze Tazim (born 1989), Turkish-Dutch actress *Zeynep Gamze Koçer (born 1998), Turkish footballer Category:Turkish feminine given names
title: Gamze
